INSERT INTO `restaurant` VALUES (11,'4 Fingers Crispy Chicken','images/4fingers_brand.jpg','9 Bishan Pi','#01-32, Junction 8','579837',1.350700,103.848801,'Crispy double fried chicken slathered in piquant garlic soy sauce, golden Kimchi Fries, refreshing Honey Yuzu drink and four fingers - all you need to a smashing meal.\n\nAt 4FINGERS, we\'re nuts about chicken, Spicy, crispy, unique and downright addictive - it\'s chicken that\'s so good, it\'s bad.',1,1,0,0,0,1,'https://www.4fingers.com/','https://www.facebook.com/gimme4fingers/','https://twitter.com/gimme4fingers?lang=en','63391327','10:30:00','22:00:00','10:30:00','22:00:00','10:30:00','22:00:00','10:30:00','22:00:00','10:30:00','22:00:00','10:30:00','22:00:00','10:30:00','22:00:00'),(12,'A&W','images/anw_brand.jpg','78 Airport Boulevard','#B2-209, Jewel Changi Airport','819666',1.360200,103.989799,'Founded in 1919, A&W stands for Allen & Wright – the two founders of an iconic American brand.\n\nThe A&W Root Beer is freshly made in-store daily, just like it was 100 years ago. Hand-crafted from a secret blend of spices, cane sugar and water, and proudly caffeine free, A&W still serves its signature root beer in an ice-cold frosty mug.\n\nExpect also international favourites such as A&W Mozza Burger, Coney Dogs, Curly Fries and Waffle Ice Cream as well as other global best-sellers world such as A&W Cream Cheese Burgers and Golden Aroma Chicken.',1,1,0,1,0,0,'https://www.awrestaurants.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/awrestaurants.sg/','https://twitter.com/awsingapore','69569898','10:00:00','23:00:00','10:00:00','23:00:00','10:00:00','23:00:00','10:00:00','23:00:00','10:00:00','23:00:00','09:00:00','23:00:00','09:00:00','23:00:00'),(13,'Bangkok Jam','images/bangkokjam_brand.jpg','68 Orchard Road','#03-85, Plaza Singapura','238839',1.300500,103.845200,'Inspired by the “City of Angels”, Bangkok, Bangkok Jam offers a modern twist to traditional Thai cuisine introducing a contemporary culinary experience to Singapore, whilst still retaining the authenticity of the well-loved cuisine. Their winning formula comprises of modern cooking techniques, notable dishes, quality and fresh ingredients as well as their stylish interior design. Signatures include their Tom Yum Fried Rice with Seafood, Grilled Chicken Thigh with Lettuce Wrap, Grilled Pork Spare Ribs with Spicy Lime Dip, and more! Other remarkable dishes that will leave you wanting more also consists of Thai Fish Cakes, Stir-fried Squid in Salted Egg Sauce, Green Papaya Salad with Soft Shell Crab, and more!\n\nJust one taste of Bangkok Jam’s show-stopping specialities, complemented with pleasant dining atmosphere and warm hospitality of the service staff, you will not even need to fly to Bangkok to be immersed in the exotic foods and gracious “smiling culture”! Come experience it for yourself today at one of Singapore’s 5 outlets island-wide!',0,0,1,0,1,0,'https://www.bangkokjam.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/BangkokJamSingapore/',NULL,'63419188','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00'),(14,'BreadTalk','images/breadtalk_brand.jpg','9 Bishan Pi','#01-35 to 36, Junction 8','579837',1.350700,103.848801,'BreadTalk is a Singaporean homegrown brand that has been imprinted fondly on Singapore’s food culture, firmly established as the go-to store for affordable and good quality variety of bread and cakes. Since its beginnings in 2000, BreadTalk honours the art of bread-making by giving life to their novel creations. They have no sign of slowing down as they continue to bring joy and goodness to satisfy every customer. \n\nBreakTalk’s premium and natural ingredients are carefully selected from global retailers such as procuring milled flour from Japan as well as pure butter from New Zealand. Pastes or fillings are made in the Central Kitchens at BreakTalk IHQ and the ingredients are specially processed from its raw states, so as to ensure greater quality control of the finished products. The best-selling buns include BreadTalk’s iconic Flosss Buns, the very bun that helped them gain traction in the hearts and tummies of many locals. There are also other creations like the Cheese Sausage and Cheese Boat buns, Bak Kwa Delight, as well as a variety of donut flavours. The products BreadTalk offers are made with a focus on creating perfect harmony among textures, flavours and ingredients. \n\nStop by a BreadTalk outlet for a taste of Singapore’s favourite bakery now!',0,0,0,1,0,1,'www.breadtalk.com.sg','https://www.facebook.com/breadtalksingapore/','https://twitter.com/sgbreadtalk','62513444','07:00:00','22:30:00','07:00:00','22:30:00','07:00:00','22:30:00','07:00:00','22:30:00','07:00:00','22:30:00','08:00:00','22:00:00','08:00:00','22:00:00'),(15,'Burger King','images/burgerKing_brand.jpg','83 Punggol Central','#01-26 , Waterway Point, East Wing ','828761',1.406800,103.902496,'Every day, more than 11 million guests visit BURGER KING restaurants around the world. And they do so because our restaurants are known for serving high-quality, great tasting, and affordable food. Founded in 1954, BURGER KING is the second largest fast food hamburger chain in the world.\n\nThe original HOME OF THE WHOPPER, our commitment to premium ingredients, signature recipes, and family-friendly dining experiences is what has defined our brand for more than 50 successful years.\n\nThe WHOPPER is America\'s favourite burger. First off a hot broiler in 1957, the WHOPPER, boasting a quarter pound of flame-grilled beef, ripe tomatoes, crisp lettuce, creamy mayo, ketchup, onions and crunchy pickles on a toasted sesame seed bun, has become an iconic burger for the ages and boasts generations of fans worldwide. There are 221,184 possible ways for a guest to order an original WHOPPER.\n\nFor those who like the taste of the WHOPPER but find it too filling, we also have the smaller version of this all time classic, the WHOPPER JR.',1,1,0,1,0,0,'https://www.burgerking.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/BurgerKingSG/','https://twitter.com/burgerkingsg','68024197','08:00:00','22:00:00','08:00:00','22:00:00','08:00:00','22:00:00','08:00:00','22:00:00','08:00:00','23:00:00','08:00:00','23:00:00','08:00:00','22:00:00'),(16,'CAFE AMAZON','images/cafeAmazon_brand.jpg','78 Airport Boulevard','#04-225, Jewel Changi Airport','819666',1.360200,103.989799,'Enjoy a fragrant cup of coffee or your favourite beverage at Cafe Amazon, a popular Thai coffee chain with over 2,000 outlets in the Land of Smiles.\n\nDesigned to be a lush oasis reminiscent of the Amazon Rainforest, the cafe is the perfect spot to relax and savour - as its slogan promises - the “Taste of Nature”.\n\nThe Jewel Changi Airport outlet is Cafe Amazon’s first flagship store outside Thailand, and features a Singapore-exclusive menu.',0,0,0,0,0,1,'https://cafeamazon.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/CafeAmazonSG/','https://twitter.com/cafeamazon1','66947028','11:00:00','21:30:00','11:00:00','21:30:00','11:00:00','21:30:00','11:00:00','21:30:00','10:00:00','21:30:00','10:00:00','21:30:00','10:00:00','21:30:00'),(17,'KFC','images/kfc_brand.jpg','681 Punggol Drive','#01-13, Oasis Terraces','820861',1.402400,103.912903,'KFC\'s irresistible flavours starts with chicken delivered fresh to our restaurants, then lovingly coated with our signature seasoning and breading resulting in chicken that is juicy, tender, and delicious to every bite! So Good!\n\nCaptivating aroma, succulent, juicy chicken and thoughtful service are what KFC lovers come back for. Choose between our signature Original Recipe chicken prepared with Colonel Sander’s secret blend of 11 herbs and spices, or the all-time favourite Hot & Crispy chicken. Visit KFC today for a dining experience that is so good.',1,1,0,1,0,0,'https://www.kfc.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/KFC.SG/','https://twitter.com/kfc_sg?lang=en','62444360','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','08:00:00','22:00:00','08:00:00','22:00:00'),(18,'McDonald\'s','images/mcdonald_brand.jpg','83 Punggol Central','#B2-07 , Waterway Point, West Wing ','828761',1.406800,103.902496,'McDonald’s is the world’s leading Quick Service Restaurant chain with the aim of becoming its customers’ favourite place and way to eat and drink. Apart from offering great-tasting, quality products like the iconic Big Mac and world-famous Fries, McDonald’s delights its customers through fast and friendly service, in a warm and welcoming environment, all at a great value. So make your way to McDonald’s for an “i’m lovin’ it” experience!\n\nMcDonald\'s provides the ultimate convenience and a haven for families. You can pop by the McCafe for a cuppa after a busy day or enjoy your favourite menu anytime with great value, all day - every day. Sink your teeth into local favourites like McSpicy or McNuggets with our signature Curry Sauce, or go for the all-time favourites like Big Mac or Filet-O-Fish.  ',1,1,0,1,0,0,'https://www.mcdonalds.com.sg/ ','https://www.facebook.com/mcdsg/','https://twitter.com/mcdonaldssgp','63857853','06:00:00','02:00:00','06:00:00','02:00:00','06:00:00','02:00:00','06:00:00','00:00:00','06:00:00','06:00:00','06:00:00','06:00:00','06:00:00','02:00:00'),(19,'Nando\'s','images/nandos_brand.jpg','68 Orchard Road','#04-10 to 11, Plaza Singapura','238839',1.300500,103.845200,'Fire up your taste buds with some PERi delicious goodness! Hailing from South Africa, Nando’s is an award-winning chain blazing across the world with its Afro-Portuguese flame-grilled PERi-PERi Chicken. In 2010, Nando’s came to Singapore and now has 6 restaurants islandwide!\n\nFew who have tried Nando’s PERi-PERi Chicken can deny the allure of its freshly grilled-to-order chicken, cooked to juicy perfection and enlivened with the fiery heat of the Nando’s PERi-PERi – the African Bird’s Eye Chili that makes the Nando’s signature sauce.\n\nNando’s chickens are fresh (never frozen) and proudly prepared in Singapore. They meet such a strict set of standards you could take them home to meet your mother. The chickens are marinated for at least 24 hours in a special PERi-PERi marinade, so the flavour goes right to the bone!\n\nReady to eat? Whether you’re feeling mild or wild, there’s a spice with your name on it - choose your PERi-PERi spice levels from 5 unique flavours: Plain…ish, Lemon & Herb, Mild, Hot and for the very brave - Extra Hot!',1,0,0,1,0,1,'https://www.nandos.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/nandosSG/','https://twitter.com/nandossg','63372555','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00','11:00:00','22:00:00'),(20,'Pastamania','images/pastamania_brand.jpg','4 Tampines Central 5','#04-21 to 22, Tampines Mall','529510',1.352500,103.944702,'Enjoy an authentic Italian dining experience right here in Singapore at Pastamania! Affordable Italian cuisine is prepared with traditional gourmet recipes, paired with the perfect restaurant ambience. Select from all-time favorites like Bacon Carbonara and Seafood Marinara and make it a meal with the Soup Of The Day or light bites! ',1,0,1,1,0,0,'https://www.pastamania.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/PastaManiaSingapore/',NULL,'67841625','11:00:00','22:30:00','11:00:00','22:30:00','11:00:00','22:30:00','11:00:00','22:30:00','11:00:00','22:30:00','11:00:00','22:30:00','11:00:00','22:30:00'),(21,'Encik Tan','images/encikTan_brand.jpg','1 Sengkang Square','#02-29, Compass One','545078',1.392000,103.895103,'Encik Tan is a casual dining chain eatery that operates under Fei Siong Group and has 20 Halal-certified outlets across heartlands in Singapore. The brand was first created to provide a range of popular local food with Halal ingredients and preparation. Not to mention, there was also a desire to preserve the nostalgic taste of the dishes, while keeping the prices affordable. Their clean and bright interior allows customers to dine in a comfortable setting while enjoying the delicious food Encik Tan offers. \n\nEncik Tan features local fares like noodles and rice, which are served quickly without compromising on its flavour and quality. Dig into their noodles offerings such as Fishball Noodles, Wonton Noodles and Chicken Meatball Noodles.Their Signature Noodles includes a mix of toppings, like fishballs, fishcakes and chicken meatball. Their Laksa is a recommended and fan favourite item at Encik Tan. Besides noodles, Curry Rice options are also available. From Chicken Cutlet and Drumsticks to seafood options like Fried Fish, Fried Prawn and Sambal Sotong sets, Encik Tan is sure to satisfy all your cravings for Singaporean delights. \n\nVisit Encik Tan for a taste of local Singaporean favourites today!',1,0,0,0,1,1,'https://enciktan.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/enciktansg/',NULL,'63701155','07:00:00','22:00:00','07:00:00','22:00:00','07:00:00','22:00:00','07:00:00','22:00:00','07:00:00','22:00:00','07:00:00','22:00:00','07:00:00','22:00:00'),(22,'stuff\'d','images/stuff_brand.jpg','21 Choa Chu Kang Ave 4','#B1-K26, LOT ONE','689812',1.385100,103.744904,'Stuff\'d prepares deliciously grilled, naturally marinated chicken hand-rolled into an exploding wrap bursting with healthy greens and flavor. Get stuffed with this delicious mix of nutritional natural goodness.',1,0,0,0,0,1,'http://stuffed.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/stuffedsg/',NULL,'67690207','10:30:00','21:45:00','10:30:00','21:45:00','10:30:00','21:45:00','10:30:00','21:45:00','10:30:00','21:45:00','10:30:00','21:45:00','10:30:00','21:45:00'),(23,'CRAVE','images/crave_brand.jpg','21 Choa Chu Kang Ave 4','#B1-K17, LOT ONE','689812',1.385100,103.744904,'CRAVE serves up the famous nasi lemak from Adam Road by Selera Rasa, matched with the best teh tarik from Rafee\'s Corner.',1,0,0,0,1,0,'https://www.crave.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/CRAVEnasilemak/',NULL,'62353048','10:00:00','22:00:00','10:00:00','22:00:00','10:00:00','22:00:00','10:00:00','22:00:00','10:00:00','22:00:00','10:00:00','22:00:00','10:00:00','22:00:00'),(24,'Andes By Astons','images/andes_brand.jpg','1 Jelubu Rd','#03-10, Bukit Panjang Plaza','677743',1.380000,103.764198,'ANDES BY ASTONS is a Halal Certified casual dining restaurant in Singapore and a spinoff of ASTONS Specialties, but it is still branded in the customary cowboy theme. ASTONS is popular for its “Value-For-Money” concept and ANDES continues to offer the best value and quality of food to all diners. \n\nANDES uses quality ingredients and provides generous portions, guaranteed to satisfy your taste buds and wallets. Their menu features an extensive selection of steak cuts, seafood and chicken with most of the main courses including 2 side dishes that diners can select from a range of options to suit their cravings. The Prime Ribeye or Sirloin is a popular choice with its succulent texture, cooked to your desired doneness, which at its inexpensive price point is definitely worth a try. The Hickory BBQ Chicken is tender and juicy, pairing nicely with the smokey and sweet Hickory sauce. There are also fish options such as their Chargrilled Salmon Fillet that is charred enticingly yet does not dry out the salmon. If one main meat is not enough for you, opt for the Super Combo that offers an extra variety, like the Surf & Turf which comes with Prime Ribeye and Prawns, also including 2 side dishes. \n\nSo if you\'re feeling the hunger pangs for hearty western grub then head down to any ANDES outlet across Singapore today. For there is definitely something to delight all!',1,0,1,1,0,0,'https://andes.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/ANDESbyAstons/',NULL,NULL,'11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00','11:30:00','22:00:00'),(25,'Anjappar','images/anjappar_brand.jpg','3 Gateway Dr','#04-08, Westgate','608532',1.334500,103.742599,'Anjappar began in 1964 in Chennai and is the trailblazer in introducing the food of Chettiars to people worldwide. The franchise set foot in Singapore in 2005 and there are currently over 50 stores all over the world. Throughout the years, Anjappar has been providing patrons a homely dining experience. \n\nHaving accumulated over 50 years of experience, Anjappar has shown their masterful use of spices to provide the best food experience for your taste buds. With secret home recipes and fresh products, Anjappar captivates food lovers with their unique dishes. One of their house specials include the Special Anjappar Chicken Dry/Masala consisting tender and boneless chicken marinated in handmade masalas and cashews, which are then roasted to taste. With the Mutton Dum Briyani, the meat is not gamey and cooked within the rice to produce an aromatic and tantalizing dish. \n\nAnjappar restaurants have managed to preserve the culinary traditions and serve as one of the most brilliant ambassadors of Chettinaad Cuisine today. Be sure to visit any Anjappar outlet in Singapore for a taste of authentic Chettinaad cuisine!',0,0,1,0,1,0,'https://www.anjappar.com.sg/','https://www.facebook.com/AnjapparSingapre/','https://twitter.com/anjapparsg','65665545','11:30:00','23:00:00','11:30:00','23:00:00','11:30:00','23:00:00','11:30:00','23:00:00','11:30:00','23:00:00','11:30:00','23:00:00','11:30:00','23:00:00');
